/**

html,

  -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
}

  position: relative;
  overflow-y: auto;
  overflow-x: hidden;
}
body {
  overflow-x: hidden;

  line-height: 45px;
}
.mobile-dialog-content {
  position: fixed;
  top: 45px;
  left: 0;
  height: calc(100% - 45px);
  width: 100%;
  overflow-x: hidden;
  overflow-y: auto;
  -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
}
.mobile-dialog_open {
  height: 100%;
  overflow: hidden !important;
}

  transform: translate3d(100vw, 0, 0);
}

  transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0);

}

}
.mobile-dialog-right-leave.mobile-dialog-right-leave-active {
  transform: translate3d(100vw, 0, 0);

}

}

  transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0);

}

}
